Package: artbenchmark
Title: Artwork Metrics Computation for Portfolio Benchmarking
Version: 0.9.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Bobby",
           family = "Fatemi",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "bfatemi07@gmail.com")
Description: Computes image-derived metrics for artwork analysis within the
    Artalytics benchmark framework. Extracts color, coverage, and complexity
    metrics from artwork images to support portfolio-relative benchmarking
    across Time & Effort, Skill & Artistry, and Complexity & Detail categories.
